Package: visPedigree
Type: Package
Title: Tidying and Visualizing Animal Pedigrees
Version: 0.5.0
Authors@R: person("Sheng","Luan", email="luansheng@foxmail.com", role = c("aut","cre"))
Description: Provides tools for tidying and visualizing animal pedigrees. The
    package performs pedigree checks for duplicated and bisexual individuals,
    detects pedigree loops, adds missing founders, sorts the pedigree, and
    traces the ancestry of candidates. It generates hierarchical graphs for
    all individuals and can handle large pedigrees (over 10,000 individuals
    per generation) by compacting full-sib groups. It is particularly
    effective for aquatic animal pedigrees, which often feature numerous
    full-sib families within nucleus breeding populations.
